Trine Bjerke Rønning (amuru 14 June 1982) bu onye egwuregwu bọọlụ Norway
Ọ gbaburu egwu maka Trondheims-Ørn na Kolbotn
Kemgbe ọ malitere otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba ụmụ nwanyị Norway na Ọktoba 1999, ọ meriri ihe karịrị otu narị na iri ise
Rønning nọchitere anya obodo ya na mbipụta 2005, 2009 na 2013 nke asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị UEFA, ka ọ bụrụ onye otu egwuregwu anaghị eme egwuregwu na 2001
Ọ gbakwara egwu na asọmpi iko mba ụwa nke 2003, 2007, 2011 na 2015 FIFA, yana n'asọmpi bọọlụ Olympic 2008
Na February 2015 a họpụtara ya onyeisi ndị otu mba.
Rønning ejirila klọb atọ dị iche iche emeriela asọmpi Toppserien Norwegian ugboro isii
Nke mbụ mụ na Trondheims-Ørn SK na 2000 na na 2001, emesia mụ na Kolbotn na 2005 na na 2006 na ọzọ ya na Stabæk FK na 2010 na 2013
Ọ meriri iko iko ụmụ nwanyị Norwegian nke mba na 1998 (dịka onye dị afọ 16), 1999, 2001 na 2002 ya na Trondheims-Ørn, dịka onye isi nke Kolbotn na 2007 yana Stabæk na 2011, 2012 na 2013
N'ime oge ise ya na Trondheims-Ørn, Rønning meriri ihe mgbaru ọsọ 40 na egwuregwu 86
Mgbe ọ chịchara Kolbotn site na oge 2007 na 2008 Rønning jụrụ ịgbatị nkwekọrịta wee sonye na otu Stabæk FK e hiwere ọhụrụ na mbido 2009
Mgbe oge 2017 gasịrị, Rønning kpebiri ịla ezumike nká.
Rønning mere mpụta mbụ ya na otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba ụmụ nwanyị Norway na Ọktoba 1999, mmeri 4–0 meriri Portugal
Na 2001 ya na ndị ntorobịa Norway ọ meriri ọlaọcha na ọnọdụ nke abụọ na asọmpi UEFA Women's Under-19
N'oge mbụ ya na ndị otu mba Rønning na-egwuri egwu n'ihe fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ ọnọdụ ọ bụla ma e wezụga onye na-eche nche
O mechara chọta ebe obibi n'ime otu na etiti azụ
Ọ gbara ndị otu Norway meriri ọlaọcha na UEFA Women's Euro 2005 na England,  wee gwụ nke anọ na 2007 FIFA World Cup na China
Norway bịakwara agba nke anọ nke asọmpi Beijing na 2008 yana Rønning dịka onye isi n'otu egwuregwu ahụ
Na 4 Septemba 2009 Rønning meriri mmerụ ikpere ka ọ gbaa egwuregwu 100th maka Norway na mmeri 3-1 nke ikpeazụ ha meriri ndị na-asọmpi Sweden na UEFA Women's Euro 2009
N'otu afọ ahụ ọ ghọrọ osote onyeisi.
Ọkachamara onye nchịkwa mba ọbụna Pellerud họpụtara Rønning na ndị otu Norway maka UEFA Women's Euro 2013 na Sweden
N'ikpeazụ na Friends Arena, o nwere ntaramahụhụ ọkara nke mbụ nke onye mgbaru ọsọ Germany bụ Nadine Angerer zọpụtara
Goolu Anja Mittag nyere ndị Germany aha nke isii ha na-esochi
Na February 2015 Rønning ka akpọrọ aha onye isi otu mba, dịka onye nọchiri anya onye merụrụ ahụ Ingvild Stensland
Ọ gbara ọkpụ goolu mbụ ndị otu ahụ n'asọmpị iko mba ụwa nke 2015, ọkpụ ọkpụ free kick na Norway meriri Thailand 4–0
Nwanne Rønning Thomas Rønning bụkwa onye egwuregwu bọọlụ nke na-egwubu Bodø/Glimt na Tippeligaen
Na January 2009, Rønning lụrụ onye otu mba otu Kristin Blystad-Bjerke, obere oge ka alụmdi na nwunye nwoke na nwanyị na Norway kwadoro
Ọnụọgụ ziri ezi dịka egwuregwu emere na Nọvemba 4, 2017
